The hotel is really beautiful, our room was spacious, very clean and had a large, modern bathroom.	Our room, a junior suite, was comfortable and the bathroom well appointed with linens and supplies.	The room was large for a European room, but there were stains on some of the furniture and there was no view from our room.	The room was well equipped and comfortable, including free internet, which was very important to me.	The bed was very comfortable and the room was clean.	The view was toward other rooms, which was just fine for an overnight stay, and very quiet.	The room was a bit small, but I suppose that is Europe.